headline: China’s Wang Yi meets Blackstone CEO amid rising trade tensions
summary: Investing.com -- China’s top diplomat Wang Yi met with Blackstone Group Chairman and CEO Stephen Schwarzman in Beijing on Thursday, emphasizing the need for peaceful coexistence between the world’s two largest economies amid escalating trade tensions.
